						<summary>

						<p>On a stone built into the front wall of the Kalamēśvara temple.</p>						

						<p>Circa 9th century.</p>						

						<p>The expression Uttarāyaṇa-saṁkrānti and Sunday only are preserved in the date portion, the other details being lost.</p>						

						<p>It records a gift of land to the temple of Īśānarāśi-bhaṭāra, by the <hi rend="italic">Mahājanas</hi> of Kāremaḍi. A portion of the gift land was to be utilised for imparting education. </p>						

						</summary>
